         <head>Existence and Location of Originals</head>
         <p>The entire collection can be located in the Art, Architecture, and Art History Theses and Projects, Yale University (RU 259).   The materials consist of research papers, theses, and projects by students in art, art history, and architecture programs at Yale.   Note: Forms part of Yale Record Group 47 (YRG 47), Collections documenting teaching and learning in Yale academic programs.</p>
         <p>HM 206 only consists of the plates for Pamela Z. Blum's thesis on the Salisbury Cathedral Chapter House</p>  
